TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CASINOLOCDETID as CASINOLOCDETID, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.PTYLOCNUM as PTYLOCNUM, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.PTYLOCNAME as PTYLOCNAME, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGM_AREA as EGM_AREA, ltrim(rtrim(D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGM_BANK)) as EGM_BANK, ltrim(rtrim(D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGM_MACHINE)) as EGM_MACHINE, ltrim(rtrim(D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.PITNUM)) as PITNUM, ltrim(rtrim(D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GAMINGTABLENUM)) as GAMINGTABLENUM, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GAMINGAREA as GAMINGAREA, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CasinoLocDesc as CasinoLocDesc, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.LocTypName as LocTypName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaName as GamingAreaName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGMAreaName as EGMAreaName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGMZoneCde as EGMZoneCde, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGMZoneDesc as EGMZoneDesc, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.EGMBankName as EGMBankName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.NumSGStns as NumSGStns, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaSeg as GamingAreaSeg, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaStrm as GamingAreaStrm, ltrim(rtrim(D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaSegName)) as GamingAreaSegName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent as MicrosRevCent, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.OperaRevCent as OperaRevCent, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaSubSeg as GamingAreaSubSeg, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SctyCde as SctyCde, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CASINOLOC as CASINOLOC, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.LOCTYPCODE as LOCTYPCODE, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.TBLAREA as TBLAREA, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SiteID as SiteID FROM D_CASINOLOCATIONDET WHERE D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.LOCTYPCODE <> 'Z'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: CASINOLOC = IN_CASINOLOC AND LOCTYPCODE = IN_LOCTYPCODE AND TBLAREA = IN_TBLAREA AND SiteID = IN_SiteID

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping populates the D_CasinoLocationDet database table with new records from the Syco/IGT Source file for CasinoLocationDetail. This data contains Casino Location information for multiple location types, i.e. VIKs, Gaming Tables, Car Park Gates, Travel, etc. representing the many and varied locations at which Gaming and Promotion Transactions occur.
MAPPING.NAME: m_CasinoLocationDet_TG

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
Decode (True, NOT ISNULL( Micros_CasinoLocDetID3), Micros_CasinoLocDetID3, CASINOLOCDETID3)
-- only if the Micros_CasinoLocDetID is not null, which means this is a Syco-sourced Outlet, already in the CDW, loaded by Micros (+PSoft) only, then replace the CasinoLocDetID with the current ID, to update the current location.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Out_CASINOLOCDETID
V_LOCTYPECODE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
--Original code only replaced nulls with '?' if tables related, all nulls need to be converted.
DECODE (RTRIM(SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail_Table_Area),NULL ,'?', UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail_Table_Area))) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_TBLAREA

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: Decode(TRUE,v_IsSydney=1 and V_LOCTYPECODE = 'T' , Decode(TRUE,upper(v_Segment)='CRYSTAL ROOM' ,'P', upper(v_Segment)='CRYSTAL SUITE' ,'V', upper(v_Segment)='CRYSTAL SALON' ,'V', upper(v_Segment)='MAHOGANY ROOM' ,'P', upper(v_Segment)='MAHOGANY SALONS' ,'V', upper(v_Segment)='SKY SALONS' ,'V', 'U' ) ,Null )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_GAMINGAREA_Sydney

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail_Property_Location_Number, '400', // Crown DECODE( SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail_Location_Type_Code, 'T' , (DECODE(V_TBLAREA,'WESTERN','R','EASTERN', 'R','VIP','V','U')) , null ), '600', //Burswood DECODE(TRUE, V_LOCTYPECODE = 'L' OR V_LOCTYPECODE = 'T' AND V_TBLAREA = 'MAIN' AND NOT (V_PITNUM = '08' OR V_PITNUM = '09'), 'R', V_LOCTYPECODE = 'T' AND V_TBLAREA = 'MAIN' AND (V_PITNUM = '08' OR V_PITNUM = '09'), 'P', V_LOCTYPECODE = 'T' AND V_TBLAREA != 'MAIN', 'V', V_LOCTYPECODE = 'T', 'U', null), '900',V_GAMINGAREA_Sydney, null )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_GAMINGAREA

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, -- Burswood Derivations v_IsBurswood = 1, DECODE(V_LOCTYPECODE, 'A', 'Travel', 'B','Beverage', 'C', 'Crown Club Booth', 'F', 'Food (includes Snack Bars)', 'G', 'Car Park Gate', 'O', 'Other (includes Retail)', 'P', 'Parking', 'R', 'Room', 'T', 'Gaming Tables', 'V', 'VIK', 'W', 'Cage / Front Window', 'L', 'Lottery', 'Unknown' ), -- Crown Derivations v_IsCrown = 1 or v_IsSydney=1, DECODE(V_LOCTYPECODE, 'A', 'Travel', 'B','Beverage', 'C', 'Crown Club Booth', 'F', 'Food (includes Snack Bars)', 'G', 'Car Park Gate', 'O', 'Other (includes Retail)', 'P', 'Parking', 'R', 'Room', 'T', 'Gaming Tables', 'V', 'VIK', 'W', 'Cage / Front Window', 'Unknown' ), -- Other Site 'Unknown')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: LocTypName

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, -- Crown Derivation v_IsCrown = 1, DECODE( SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail_Location_Type_Code, 'T' , (DECODE(V_TBLAREA, 'WESTERN','Regular Gaming', 'EASTERN', 'Regular Gaming', 'VIP','VIP Gaming', 'INTL', 'VIP Gaming', 'PEARL', 'VIP Gaming', 'Unknown')) , 'U', 'Unknown',null ), -- Burswood Derivations v_IsBurswood, DECODE(V_GAMINGAREA, 'R', 'Regular Gaming', 'V', 'Pearl (VIP)', 'P', 'Premium', 'U', 'Unknown'), v_IsSydney=1, DECODE(V_GAMINGAREA, 'P', 'Premium', 'V', 'VIP Gaming', 'U', 'Unknown'), null)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GamingAreaName

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SiteID, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CASINOLOCDETID, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CASINOLOC, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.LOCTYPCODE, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaName, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaSeg, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaStrm, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.GamingAreaSegName FROM D_CASINOLOCATIONDET WHERE D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent<>'?' and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent is not null and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.TblNum is null and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SiteID=$$SiteID ORDER BY D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SiteID, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent, D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.CASINOLOCDETID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent<>'?' and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.MicrosRevCent is not null and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.TblNum is null and D_CASINOLOCATIONDET.SiteID=$$SiteID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: P_CASINOLOC = S_CASINOLOC AND P_LOCTYPCODE = S_LOCTYPECODE AND P_SiteID = S_SiteID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This transform will get the record with max(CasinoLocDetID) for each MicrosRevCent,SiteID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((NOT ISNULL(M_CASINOLOCDETID)) and M_LOCTYPCODE='X', M_CASINOLOCDETID, null)

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: Decode (True, -- if found the relative Parking location and the already loaded GamingAreaName is not null NOT ISNULL(P_GamingAreaName), P_GamingAreaName, -- if found the relative Micros location, and the already loaded GamingAreaName is not null NOT ISNULL(M_GamingAreaName), M_GamingAreaName, S_GamingAreaName )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GamingAreaName

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: Decode (True, -- if found the relative Parking location and the already loaded GamingAreaSeg is not null NOT ISNULL(P_GamingAreaSeg), P_GamingAreaSeg, -- if found the relative Micros location, and the already loaded GamingAreaSeg is not null NOT ISNULL(M_GamingAreaSeg), M_GamingAreaSeg, --S_GamingAreaSeg iif(isnull(S_GamingAreaSeg),null,S_GamingAreaSeg) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GamingAreaSeg

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: Decode (True, -- if found the relative Parking location and the already loaded GamingAreaSegName is not null NOT ISNULL(P_GamingAreaSegName), P_GamingAreaSegName, -- if found the relative Micros location, and the already loaded GamingAreaSegName is not null NOT ISNULL(M_GamingAreaSegName), M_GamingAreaSegName, --S_GamingAreaSegName iif(isnull(S_GamingAreaSegName),null,S_GamingAreaSegName) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GamingAreaSegName

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: Decode (True, -- if found the relative Micros location, and the already loaded GamingAreaStrm is not null NOT ISNULL(M_GamingAreaStrm), M_GamingAreaStrm, --S_GamingAreaStrm iif(isnull(S_GamingAreaStrm),null,S_GamingAreaStrm) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GamingAreaStrm

SHORTCUT.COMMENTS: Flat file extracted from SYCO containing Casino Location Detail data.
SHORTCUT.NAME: Shortcut_To_SYCO_CasinoLocationDetail

SHORTCUT.COMMENTS: The locations where customer interaction takes place within the property. This includes the locations of gaming products (gaming tables and electronic gaming machines (EGM) ), food and beverage venues (restaurants, bars, snack bars), car park booths / gates, Crown Club booths, VIKs (Voucher Issuance Kiosks), etc. Some locations belong to a hierarchy / grouping. For example, a specific EGM is located within a bank of machines which in turn is located within an area. The EGM location copde of A0203 thus indicates that this is machine 03 located within bank 02 located within area A.
SHORTCUT.NAME: Shortcut_To_D_CASINOLOCATIONDET
